txt.en: 'If we are to bring people here and turn this into a true town of Rohan, they must have suitable places to call home and to live. Much of the town was burnt, including the houses and cottages, during the raid. Getting the base woodwork replaced and repaired is a good starting point.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
